sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Host
    participant GE as game_engine
    actor PL as Players

    H->>GE: start_game
    GE->>H: question {scoring_rule, time_limit_sec} (BroadcastAll)
    GE->>PL: question {scoring_rule, time_limit_sec} (BroadcastAll)

    Note over GE: countdown timer (time_limit_sec)

    alt Player answers before timer
        PL->>GE: submit_answer
        GE->>GE: scoring_rule.calculate_points(elapsed, time_limit_sec)
        GE-->>PL: answer_result (PlayerOnly)
    end

    alt Host closes early
        H->>GE: end_question
    else Timer expires naturally
        Note over GE: sleep(time_limit_sec) completes
    end

    GE->>H: question_ended {correct_index, leaderboard} (BroadcastAll)
    GE->>PL: question_ended {correct_index, leaderboard} (BroadcastAll)
